title: 11/12/20 DPS-BEST OF
itunes:title: 11/12/20 DPS-BEST OF
description:
On today's episode of the Dan Patrick Show, DP discusses some of the cancellations of games we've seen throughout College Football for this weekend. What will be the trickle down effect from it? Will the SEC continue to lead the way for how the rest of the College Football season will play out? We're joined by Former NFL Linebacker and FS1's Emmanuel Acho, Sports Illustrated Senior Writer Ross Dellenger and Ohio State's Head Football Coach Ryan Dyan. Plus, DP delves in to the sand used at the Masters.
